# Simple Image Classifiers

Minimal JS interface to an image classifer deployed in Hugging Face Spaces 
- [Dog vs. Cat Classifier](https://huggingface.co/spaces/prasanthntu/dog-vs-cat-classifier). For full screen version, refer this [link](https://prasanthntu-dog-vs-cat-classifier.hf.space/)
- [Who is the SuperHero Classifier](https://huggingface.co/spaces/prasanthntu/who-is-the-hero). For full screen version, refer this [link](https://prasanthntu-who-is-the-hero.hf.space/)

## Curl examples
- To convert images to base64, use https://www.base64-image.de/
- To convert base64 strong to image, use https://codebeautify.org/base64-to-image-converter#
